onal football team|Poland]]\n| nationalcaps1 =    29  \n| nationalgoals1 =   7 \n|            club-update = \n|            ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Stanis\u0142aw Andrzej \"Stan\" Terlecki''' (13 November 1955  \u2013 28 December 2017<ref>[http://www.dziennikbaltycki.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/a/nie-zyje-stanislaw-terlecki-wybitny-pilkarz-lks-lodz-i-reprezentant-polski-mial-62-lata,12801780/ Nie \u017cyje Stanis\u0142aw Terlecki. Wybitny pi\u0142karz \u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a i reprezentant Polski mia\u0142 62 lata]</ref>) was a [[Poland|Polish]] [[association football|footballer]].\n\nHe played a total of 29 games for [[Poland national football team|Poland]], scoring 7 goals.<ref>[http://www.kadra.pl/index.php?strona=historia&dzial=reprezentanci&litera=S Kadra.pl] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210204903/http://kadra.pl/index.php?strona=historia&dzial=reprezentanci&litera=S |date=10 February 2012 }}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Ok\u0119cie Airport incident]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.nasljerseys.com/Players/T/Terlecki.Stan.htm NASL career stats]\n* {{90minut|2200}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Terlecki, Stanislaw}}\n[[Category:1955 births]]\n[[Category:2017 deaths]]\n[[Category:San Jose Earthquakes (1974\u20131988) players]]\n[[Category:\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a players]]\n[[Category:Legia Warsaw players]]\n[[Category:Major Indoor Soccer League (1978\u20131992) players]]\n[[Category:North American Soccer League (1968\u20131984) players]]\n[[Category:North American Soccer League (1968\u20131984) indoor players]]\n[[Category:New York Cosmos players]]\n[[Category:Pittsburgh Spirit players]]\n[[Category:Polish expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Polish footballers]]\n[[Category:Poland international footballers]]\n[[Category:Polonia Warsaw players]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Warsaw]]\n[[Category:Gwardia Warszawa players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Poland-footy-midfielder-stub}}\n{{Poland-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2017}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|          name      = Stanis\u0142aw Terlecki\n|               image = \n|            fullname = Stanis\u0142aw Andrzej Terlecki\n|         birth_date = {{birth date|1955|11|13|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Warsaw]], [[Poland]]\n| death_date          = {{Death date and age|df=yes|2017|12|28|1955|11|13}}\n| death_place         = [[\u0141\u00f3d\u017a]], Poland\n|              height = \n|            position = [[Midfielder]] / [[Striker (association football)|Striker]]\n|         currentclub = \n|          clubnumber = \n| youthyears1 =   \n| youthclubs1 =   \n|  years1 =   1972\u20131973 \n| years2 =  1973\u20131975 \n| years3 =  1975\u20131981 \n| years4 =  1981\u20131983 \n| years5 =  1983 \n| years6 =  1983\u20131984 \n| years7 =  1984 \n| years8 =  1984\u20131986 \n| years9 =  1986\u20131988 \n| years10 =  1988\u20131989 \n| years11 =  1989\u20131990 \n| years12 =  1991 \n| years13 =  1991\u20131993\n|  clubs1 =   [[Polonez Warszawa]] \n| clubs2 =  [[Gwardia Warszawa]] \n| clubs3 =  [[\u0141\u00f3dzki KS]] \n| clubs4 =  [[Pittsburgh Spirit]] (indoor) \n| clubs5 =  [[San Jose Earthquakes (NASL)|Golden Bay Earthquakes]] \n| clubs6 =  [[New York Cosmos (1971\u20131985)|New York Cosmos]] (indoor) \n| clubs7 =  [[New York Cosmos (1971\u20131985)|New York Cosmos]] \n| clubs8 =  [[Pittsburgh Spirit]] (indoor) \n| clubs9 =  [[\u0141\u00f3dzki KS]] \n| clubs10 =  [[Legia Warsaw]] \n| clubs11 =  [[St. Louis Storm]] (indoor) \n| clubs12 =  [[\u0141\u00f3dzki KS]] \n| clubs13 =  [[Polonia Warsaw]]\n| caps1 =             \n| caps2 =   \n| caps3 =   \n| caps4 =  88  \n| caps5 =  27   \n| caps6 =   \n| caps7 =  17  \n| caps8 =  62   \n| caps9 =   \n| caps10 =   \n| caps11 =  39   \n| goals1 =  \n| goals2 =  \n| goals3 =  \n| goals4 =  139  \n| goals