ers are equipped with laser guns to shoot the scenery and gain points.\n| [[Duel (ride)|The Haunted House]]\n|-\n| [[Hex \u2013 The Legend of the Towers|Hex - The Legend<br>of the Towers]] || {{NA|}} [[File:Alton Towers - Hex.jpg|120px]] ||Walk-through/<br>Madhouse dark ride combination\n|Operational|| 2000 || The Towers || [[Vekoma]] ||style=\"text-align:left\" | A walkthrough attraction based on the legend of the chained oak. Concludes with a Madhouse attraction in the ride's Vault area.\n| N/A\n|-\n| [[Gangsta Granny: The Ride]] || {{NA|}}|| Dark ride\n|Operational|| 2020 || The World of David Walliams || [[Garmendale Engineering]] ||style=\"text-align:left\" | A dark ride based on the story of Gangsta Granny, written by David Walliams.\n| [[Wobble World]]\n|}\n\n=== Children's rides ===\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:8em;\"| Name !! Picture !! Type !! Opened !!  scope=\"col\" style=\"width:8em;\"| Area !! style=\"width:10em;\" |Manufacturer !! ! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:25em;\" class=\"unsortable\"| Additional information|!!Replaced\n|-\n| [[Driving School (Alton Towers)|Cuckoo Cars Driving School]] ||   {{NA|}} [[File:Alton towers driving school.jpg|110px]] ||align=center | Driving Attraction || 2006 || style=\"text-align: center\" |Currently Unknown || style=\"text-align: center\" |SB International AB || style=\"text-align:left\" | A children's car driving attraction.\n| Vintage Cars\n|-\n| Raj's Bouncy Bottom Burp   ||  {{NA|}} ||align=center | [[Drop Tower|Mini drop tower]] || style=\"text-align: center\" | 1999 <br/><small>(2020 as Raj's Bouncy Bottom Burp)</small> || style=\"text-align: center\" | The World of David Walliams || style=\"text-align: center\" |[[S&S - Sansei Technologies|S&S Power]]|| style=\"text-align:left\" | A mini [[drop tower]] for children.\n| Frog Hopper\n|-\n| Royal Carousel (Formerly Gallopers Carousel) ||   {{NA|}} [[File:Alton towers carousel.jpg|110px]] ||alig